item.description: About Me I am currently a Ph.D. student at the University of California, Santa Cruz in the Computer Science and Engineering department. I graduated from the National Institute of Technology, Durgapur in 2020 with a Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science and Engineering. Research Interests Storage systems Distributed systems Cloud computing Contact Email: jayjeetc@ucsc.edu LinkedIn: jayjeetc Github: JayjeetAtGithub Office: Room 375, Engineering 2, BSOE, UC Santa Cruz. Taking a nap under a tree once helped a guy solve the universe.
